These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, coffee, iced-tea, lemonade
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, goldfish, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, scooter, taxi, train
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person drinking water is the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | coffee  | lemonade | iced-tea    | water       |
| Pet         | hamster | snake    | goldfish      | turtle |
| Transport   | ship   | taxi | scooter | train        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, potato, zucchini, raspberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, accountant, analyst, paramedic
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, taxi, van, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the paramedic##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the analyst is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the tram is the writer##1
6. the person driving the bus is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | zucchini   | potato | kale     | raspberry      |
| Job         | accountant | analyst | paramedic | writer |
| Transport   | taxi    | bus   | van     | tram      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, hiking, fishing, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, folk, techno, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, australian, dutch
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of techno##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the fan of folk##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the australian##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | traveling | hiking | fishing | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | folk    | disco | techno     |
| Nationality   | japanese | australian    | dutch | mexican    |

