.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, paramedic, manager, social-worker
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball, skiing, lacrosse
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bike, roller, scooter
1. the manager is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the paramedic is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is the manager##1
7. the manager is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | security-guard | social-worker | manager | paramedic |
| Sport       | basketball     | lacrosse      | biathlon     | skiing      |
| Transport   | bike | car         | scooter      | roller        |

