.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, photography, baking, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, comedy, zombie, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skiing, swimming, cricket
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | baking   | fishing | photography  | board-games      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie  | superhero        | fantasy  | comedy       |
| Sport         | weightlifting | swimming    | skiing | cricket |

