.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, scientist, security-guard, freelancer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, comedy, adventure, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, classical, soul
1. the journalist is the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the freelancer##1
4. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
5. the scientist is on the far left##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is the security-guard##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
8. the freelancer is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | scientist | security-guard | freelancer | journalist |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | adventure  | comedy | epic   |
| Music-Genre   | soul   | d&b     | classical | gospel       |

