.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, watermelon, pomegranate, cauliflower
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, magic-tricks, board-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy, comedy, time-travel
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1
2. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | broccoli  | cauliflower | pomegranate   | watermelon     |
| Hobby         | board-games | drawing   | woodworking  | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy         | martial-arts  | fantasy | time-travel  |

