.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, 7up, milk, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, western, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: british, japanese, indonesian, italian
1. the person drinking 7up is the indonesian##1
2. the italian is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the indonesian##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
6. the italian is the person drinking milk##1
7. the japanese is on the left of the italian##1
8. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | water | milk     | cola | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | musical | western       | disaster    |
| Nationality   | japanese   | italian | british    | indonesian |

