.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, corn, pineapple, lime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, gospel, soul, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, surfing, skiing, baseball
1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person eating corn##1
5. the person eating corn is on the right of the fan of classical##1
6. the fan of classical is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | pineapple        | lime   | corn  | raspberry   |
| Music-Genre   | rock         | classical     | gospel    | soul       |
| Sport         | surfing | biathlon | skiing | baseball |

