.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, cola, water
There 4 different types of food: lime, garlic, kale, lemon
4 different pets are kept: fish, goldfish, dog, hedgehog
1. the person drinking water is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person eating kale is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
7. the person eating lime is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | cola | water | milk        |
| Food       | lemon | lime  | garlic | kale     |
| Pet        | goldfish    | dog   | hedgehog  | fish |

