.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, scientist, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, soccer, badminton, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, taxi, ship
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the firefighter##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the fisherman##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's sport is badminton is the pilot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | pilot  | fisherman | firefighter  | scientist |
| Sport       | badminton | soccer        | handball | parkour       |
| Transport   | quad-bike   | subway          | ship          | taxi       |

