.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, collecting, sudoku, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, time-travel, superhero, musical
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, thai, brazilian, chinese
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the chinese is on the left of the egyptian##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is the brazilian##1
7. the chinese is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku   | video-games | collecting |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy | time-travel   | musical |
| Nationality   | chinese     | egyptian  | brazilian  | thai  |

