.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, magic-tricks, video-games, fishing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, d&b, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, handball, baseball
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fan of disco##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of disco##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the fan of folk##1
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | fishing | magic-tricks    | skydiving        | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | d&b     | disco        | dubstep   |
| Sport         | rowing   | ice-hockey | handball | baseball  |

