2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the australian##1
3. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the argentine##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
7. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
8. the dutch is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | family  | time-travel    | thriller    |
| Nationality   | australian | argentine  | brazilian  | dutch |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | skateboard | airplane | scooter        |

