.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, milk, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, adventure, action, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, tennis, badminton, rowing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person watching western movies is the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person drinking cola is the person watching disaster movies##1
8. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola        | sprite    | mirinda | milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster        | western   | adventure  | action  |
| Sport         | rowing | tennis | badminton   | skiing |

