4. the person eating lettuce is the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person watching epic movies is the person eating blueberry##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
