The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, water-polo, volleyball, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, jet-ski
1. the nigerian is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the indian##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the german is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian | german | brazilian |
| Sport         | water-polo | biathlon | swimming  | volleyball  |
| Transport     | airplane  | bike | jet-ski     | car  |

