.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, dancer, mechanic, lawyer
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, australian, italian, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, cricket, rowing, climbing
1. the dancer is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the mechanic##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
4. the italian is on the far right##1
5. the dutch is the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the lawyer is on the far right##1
8. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | dancer  | mechanic  | police-officer | lawyer |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch | australian   | italian      |
| Sport         | volleyball | rowing    | cricket   | climbing         |

 